description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Min Calisthenics Workout | No Equipment | All Levels' from the channel Vitality.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Get ready for this 20 min full body Calisthenics workout which will prepare you for skills like the human flag, planche, any lever etc. The exercises target specifically the muscle groups engaged in these Calisthenics skills (and many more).

You can do this full body workout at home and without any equipment! No bars, no parallettes etc. needed. The only thing you need is yourself. Do every exercise with the full range of motion and focus on eccentric (negative) movements. This will boost your gains and progress tremendously.

Give your best - 40 sec full energy, 20 sec rest!
